<p>You have earlier seen how enterprises are organising themselves in the digital and multicloud world and the four kind of organizations thus forming.</p>

<p>Within each of these elements, there are various functions that support product development and operations:</p>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th style="text-align: center"><strong>4 Pillars Function</strong></th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
